data.description: If you are looking for a unique and secluded home, then look no more.  This home is on a 1.6 acresdoor  surrounded by nature.  It is close proximity to major highways.  The house is 3 bedrooms and 3 full bathrooms with fully finished basement.  It includes an oversized 3 car garage with built ins and storage.   Newly remodeled kitchen with stainless steel appliances; gas stove, quartz countertop with 4 stools, a large island with a wine cooler, farm kitchen sink, new flooring, recess lights and lighting fixtures and lots of storage spaces.  Living room with cathedral ceiling, gas fireplace, wood beams, recess lights and ceiling fans.  Freshly painted bedrooms with hardwood floors.  The main bathroom is with whirlpool tub and separate shower.  Back deck freshly varnished.  Water filtration installed in 2020 and also septic system upgrades.   Installation of the Solar panels average electric bills are $35 per month.  There is a water well therefore no water bill.  The list goes on and on.   This is a must-see opportunity for a family.
